title: SD Replay: Side Effects of Being a Cancer
description:
This week, in honor of my birthday, we're bringing back an episode from last year for the uber sensitive, oh so loyal, consummate homebodies, THE CANCERS! It's all about the crybaby creatives of the zodiac, and what’s it’s like to be us, know us, and love us!
